edu.ucla.sspace.tools

Class DependencyBasisMaker.OccurrenceCounter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.tools.DependencyBasisMaker.OccurrenceCounter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticSpace
    Enclosing class:
    DependencyBasisMaker

    public class DependencyBasisMaker.OccurrenceCounter
extends Object
implements SemanticSpace
    A simple term SemanticSpace implementation that counts word co-occurrences, performs a transform, and then scores each recorded basis dimension based on the row summed scores for each word.

        public void processSpace(Properties properties)
        Once all the documents have been processed, performs any post-processing steps on the data. An algorithm should treat this as a no-op if no post-processing is required. Callers may specify the values for any exposed parameters using the properties argument.
